collectible.name: The Philosopher
collectible.description:
26/100 | Gen 1 | Legendary

The Philosopher is a adjunct Professor of Philosophy at the Federal University of Amapá. Researcher in the field of Metaphysics. Editor of the Philosophical Investigation Series. Coordinator of the Philosophical Investigation Channel. Leader of the Philosophical Investigation Research Group, member of the Analytical Metaphysics WG at ANPOF, Society for the Metaphysics of Science and the Laboratory of Applied Studies in Infoproducts. Former Editor-in-Chief of the journal Investigation Filosófica (2010-2020). Post-Doctoral Residence in Philosophy held at the Federal University of Minas Gerais. Doctor and Master in Logic and Metaphysics (Philosophy) by the Postgraduate Program in Logic and Metaphysics at the Federal University of Rio de Janeiro, with a sandwich period at the University Catholique de Louvain. Bachelor of Philosophy from the Federal University in Ouro Preto. The Philosopher clearly does a lot!

collectible.name: Architect Island: Plan
collectible.description:
Scarcity gnomes have begun to travel to other islands. They noticed the Architect Island permanent structures and editable interiors are up for sale: https://opensea.io/assets/cryptovoxels?search[stringTraits][0][name]=island&search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=Architect%20Island&search[sortAscending]=true&search[sortBy]=PRICE

This blueprint work station was smuggled back from the Plan suburb in the South by a seafaring Water gnome. The Architects there are https://twitter.com/lilpaats and https://twitter.com/FORRMArchitects. Secrets and origins of the island layout are known mainly to LilPaats if you dare quest again to inquire more.

You can visit the location here: https://www.voxels.com/play?coords=SE@1128E,867N

collectible.name: CV Wearable 1/1: The Philosopher Bistrot - K-Food Series #08 - Purple Heart Chair
collectible.description: This piece of furniture was specially created by The Chef and branded by The Philosopher, to inhabit their restaurant. The chair cushions are made of artificial goose feather and provide a completely soft and comfortable seat and back for you to have a great meal. One of its meta-material is Purple Heart, a type of wood that is obtained from the tree called Peltogyne, which is only available in Central South America and rainy forests. One of the most expensive woods in the world. If you also want the rendered tezos MP4, please visit our Voxel Dreams store on Hic et Nunc: https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/Voxel_Dreams/creations

collectible.name: CV Wearable 1/1: The Philosopher Bistrot #12: Risoto de Disco, by DJ The Chef
collectible.description:
From peddlers, traveling salesman, truckers and nomadic troops, ´Risoto de Disco´ is a delicacy prepared with various ingredients in the plow disc (truck rim). Childhood memories of the author bring colors and confortfood flavours on this voxel dish. DJ The Chef (a.k.a. wasem_simon) teaches a tasty recipe that yields many servings.


Risoto de Disco - The Brazilian Disco Risotto - vegetarian version
4 farms of rice
1 kg of cassava
1 red pepper (seedless)
1 large onion
2 garlic cloves
4 ripe tomatoes (seedless)
green seasoning to taste (parsley, chives, mangerone)

If you want to collect the audio-visual file, please visit our store on Tezos at: https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/Voxel_Dreams

Created by DJ The Chef and branded by The Philosopher.

collectible.name: Scarcity: Dead Skeleton Dark Gnome
collectible.description: This souless necromancer dark faction gnome was dead when fighting the great mystical dragons who ended the great war. Many dark gnomes were killed in this event, and their bodies were buried underground, in Scarcity, near their treasures, as an homage to their heroic attempt of saving all the factions. But Anubis ressurrected some necromancers, so you can also find some of them undead imprisoned into the glitch galleries.
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b

collectible.name: Scarcity: Adam, Necro's Son: becoming an undead
collectible.description: Adam has just lived for a day before dying with his mother. This is the scene where Anubis starts the ritual to turn Adam into his servant. He decided for himself to be part of Anubis' Army. As a servant of Anubis Justice, Adam rules all over the souls, including the souls of his family.
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b

collectible.name: Scarcity: Cynthia, Necro's Wife
collectible.description: No living person knows how Cynthia was before she died, but now she is resurrected as an undead. She still have feelings for her husband and son, but  the zombie feelings are pretty strong sometimes, and it was hard to live a happy life, until Necro accepted to join her in the underworld, with their son. Now they are fighting against their old brothers from Scarcity, in the name of Anubis, but at least they are a family again.
